attached to the boot disk (whole-disk, off-box)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#eef3fb,#1f2a38);strokeColor=#5A6B7B;fontColor=#1A1A1A;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="bk"><mxGeometry x="24" y="356" width="260" height="62" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="warn3" value="Verified caveats:
• Declared container limits sum to 3.5 vCPU / 3.4 GB on a
   2 vCPU / 4 GB host — deliberately oversubscribed.
• cverify-core depends_on cverify-ai: service_healthy, but
   cverify-ai declares NO healthcheck (docker-compose.yml).
• ~/backups lives on the same boot disk as the data it backs up;
   the GCE disk snapshot is the only off-box copy.
• Images are built on the VM by `docker compose up --build`.
   There is no container registry in this deployment." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#f8cecc,#5a2b28);strokeColor=#B85450;fontColor=#1A1A1A;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="b2"><mxGeometry x="366" y="38" width="260" height="188" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="ed1" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;rounded=0;jettySize=auto;orthogonalLoop=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=light-dark(#1B2733,#CFE0F0);strokeColor=light-dark(#2D6A9F,#5B9BD5);strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="k_pg" target="v_pg"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="ed2" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;rounded=0;jettySize=auto;orthogonalLoop=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=light-dark(#1B2733,#CFE0F0);strokeColor=light-dark(#2D6A9F,#5B9BD5);strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="k_redis" target="v_redis"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="ed3" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;rounded=0;jettySize=auto;orthogonalLoop=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=light-dark(#1B2733,#CFE0F0);strokeColor=light-dark(#2D6A9F,#5B9BD5);strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="k_ai" target="v_ws"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="1184" y="530"/><mxPoint x="1017" y="530"/><mxPoint x="1017" y="722"/><mxPoint x="1056" y="722"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="ed4" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;rounded=0;jettySize=auto;orthogonalLoop=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=light-dark(#1B2733,#CFE0F0);strokeColor=light-dark(#2D6A9F,#5B9BD5);strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edg